The evidence with the title 'Remarks by the president in State Of The Union address ... ' says Jan 24, 2012  ... In the six months before i took office , we lost nearly 4 million jobs. And we lost another 4 million before our policies were in full effect. Those are the facts. But so are these: in the last 22 months, businesses have created more than 3 million jobs. (applause.) Last year, they created the most jobs since 2005. 
